Data Description
The data was scraped from the following websites using WebDriver:
http://www.acfun.tv/v/list96/index.htm

The format of the data:
Timestamp: the time of the comment relative to the video (in seconds)
Comment: the actual comment text 
User_id: the user id of the user that posts this comment
Date_time: actual date of the comment in Unix time
Fonts: font of the comment displayed on screen
Size: size of the texts of the comment
Color: color of the texts of the comment

Size of the data:
8 Genres: Action, Animation, Crime, Drama, Fantasy,Historical, Horror, Romance
80 Movies: 10 movies for each genres (chosen based on high IMDB scores)
240000 comments: each movie has around 3000~8000 comments.


